title: Looking For a support, jungle or top
body:
Hey guys looking for a Support, Jungle or Top not all three one or the other please, for a semi serious and good vibed ranked team. Silver to plat rank is preferred but not nessacary. If these are your mains  feel free to add me so we can talk. A working mic is Essential
Thanks for you time.

replies.body: All postions filled however i will be accpeting subs for mid top adc and jungle
For top, I would be interested. Let me know. Cheers
